<plot>Mood swings and memory loss, not to mention hot flashes, night sweats, sleeplessness, are just some of the symptoms of which the mere mention would make anyone cringe. Now is the time to speak up and reveal the truths behind what our popular culture has been so silent about "The Change,". From what menopause actually is and how it works, to what the symptoms are and how they affect a woman's life and the lives of the people around her.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?246409</url></doc>
